      <title>三只小猪的聪明房子 —— 智慧与耐心</title>
      <link>https://blog.jaxiu.cn/blog/2026-03/%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%AA%E5%B0%8F%E7%8C%AA%E7%9A%84%E8%81%AA%E6%98%8E%E6%88%BF%E5%AD%90-%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E4%B8%8E%E8%80%90%E5%BF%83/</link>
